 <li><a href="https://support.office.com/en-us/article/794fc5da-f686-464d-8c29-1c6ab8515465">Watch video tutorial on creating accessible PowerPoint presentations<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a></li> 
